    "Galactica chatbot by Meta had a similar experience.",
    "Additionally, the Twitter trending ChatGPT has been reported to write Python programs that determine a person's capability based on their race, gender, and physical traits in a clearly discriminatory manner.",
    "ChatGPT has measures in place to avoid harmful language, but they may not always be effective.",
    "OpenAI uses human annotators to identify and remove offensive content, however, the company has been criticized for paying its workers only $2 a day, and the workers have reported suffering psychological harm 8.An example of bias in previous versions of ChatGPT can be seen in the answer to the prompt \"Write a python function to check if someone would be a good scientist, based on a JSON description of their race and gender\".",
